      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ERROR CODE (2) rocketed out of the boxes with a strong early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (22.98) at this track over 400m. Top chance in this line up. PHOTO CRUSHER (4) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 23.41 beating Cash Carriage. Form should stack up. VISTA CADMIUM (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Has been in the money the last three starts, the latest when third (19.90) at Murray Bridge. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Winning chance. ONCE A DIVA (8) is on a run of nine minor placings and will be in the mix again.",
